{"tid":2357367,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"知名企業陸續來港上市 今年不能錯過的5大新股","createTime":"2021-01-07T11:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T11:29:50.000Z","uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"05934d09da6af992b45e9b0dfbf21ef2f23cc4d4","tid":2357367,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2845000/2846717/324_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2845000%2F2846717%2F324_1024.jpeg&h=36871b3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">快手（最快農曆新年前招股）</span></span></strong><br />\n短視頻平台快手擬在下周尋求上市聆訊。報道有指，公司最快於農曆新年前進行招股。據內地媒早前報道，公司計劃於今年2月5日掛牌，有承銷商透露，目標估值達500億美元（約3,900億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">百度（2021年上半年上市）</span></span></strong><br />\n據彭博報道，百度（美：BUDI）計劃最快今年上半年來港第二上市。報道指，百度已選擇中信里昂證券和高盛幫助安排上市事宜，集資規模35億美元（約273億港元）。若公司成功上市，將形成「BAT」齊集香港格局。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">嗶哩嗶哩（最快本周或下周初遞交上市申請）</span></span></strong><br />\n內地視頻平台嗶哩嗶哩（BILIBILI）（美：BILI）準備來港第二上市，最快在本周末或下周初申請香港公開發售。嗶哩嗶哩集資額可能超過20億美元（約155億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">京東物流（最快今年第二至第三季上市）</span></span></strong><br />\n京東  （09618）  分拆京東物流再有新進展。據外電引述知情人士指，京東物流已委聘美林及高盛為上市負責行，公司計劃集資約40億美元（約312億港元），最快於今年第二至第三季上市，其估值可能達到400億美元（約3120億元）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">滴滴出行（年內來港上市）</span></span></strong><br />\n滴滴出行擬於今年內來港上市。據內地媒體報道，一站式移動出行及生活服務平台滴滴出行目標估值介乎600億至800億美元（約4680億至6240億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n據公司網頁顯示，滴滴出行在亞太區、拉美、俄羅斯擁有超過5.5億用戶提供出租車召車、網約車、順風車、公交、共享單車、共享電單車、代駕、汽車服務、配送及貨運、金融等多元化服務。單計去年10月首周，公司業務單日量超過6000萬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新中國五寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7e53f39bced5cc24dcab46b792cfc06f6712e7","tid":2357367,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:18:23.000Z","msg":"想入快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06f97153f3e5fa3841c08a019f6e388b85c1f59","tid":2357367,"uid":262746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:20:12.000Z","msg":"9988之流，呢啲垃圾陰質野，等媽咪面抽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51eaf8a15eaf9b29297e17af9c69e8b11c919247","tid":2357367,"uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f06f97153f3e5fa3841c08a019f6e388b85c1f59","tid":2357367,"uid":262746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:20:12.000Z","msg":"9988之流，呢啲垃圾陰質野，等媽咪面抽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YSReCDd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYSReCDd.png&h=46af6da4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n係中國公司垃圾定係恆指不思進取唔肯接受新事物?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e921039e97bf0ce8ee69ea002a1f1d414c45f3db","tid":2357367,"uid":262746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51eaf8a15eaf9b29297e17af9c69e8b11c919247","tid":2357367,"uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f06f97153f3e5fa3841c08a019f6e388b85c1f59","tid":2357367,"uid":262746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:20:12.000Z","msg":"9988之流，呢啲垃圾陰質野，等媽咪面抽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YSReCDd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYSReCDd.png&h=46af6da4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n係中國公司垃圾定係恆指不思進取唔肯接受新事物?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:29:50.000Z","msg":"港股加中資問題"}]}